to run pig scripts use
pig <script name>(they are run in mapreduce mode)

pig q1.pig
pig q2.pig
pig q3.pig
pig q4.pig


to run hive scripts use
hive -f <script name>

hive -f q5.hive
hive -f q6.hive
hive -f q7.hive
hive -f q8.hive
hive -f q9.hive



Note: I could not find the datasets in cluster.
Hence i have run all the problems in local machine.

To run above scripts in cluster might need to change paths
in q1 to q4.pig scripts.

